<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    1. Introduction At GlamourTime, we value and respect the privacy of our users. This privacy policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.

    2. Information We Collect We collect the following information:

    Personal Information: Name, email address, phone number, etc.
    Usage Information: Data on how you use our website, including pages visited and time spent on each page.
    Technical Information: IP address, browser type, operating system, etc.
    3. Use of Information We use the collected information to:

    Provide and improve our services.
    Personalize the user experience.
    Send promotional communications and updates.
    Analyze website usage to enhance functionality.
    4. Sharing Information We do not share your personal information with third parties, except in the following circumstances:

    With your explicit consent.
    To comply with legal obligations.
    With service providers who help us operate our website and are subject to confidentiality obligations.
    5. Information Security We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.

    6. Cookies and Similar Technologies We use cookies and similar technologies to improve website functionality and personalize your experience. You can set your browser to reject cookies, but this may affect your ability to use some features of the site.

    7. User Rights You have the right to:

    Access your personal information.
    Request the correction of incorrect information.
    Request the deletion of your personal information.
    Object to the processing of your personal information.
    8. Changes to the Privacy Policy We reserve the right to update this privacy policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page and, if significant, we will notify you by email.

    9. Contact If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, you can contact us at: [contact email].
</p>
